data.description: Check out this price adjustment!! Don’t miss out on this one-of-a-kind CUSTOM-BUILT POOL/SPA home located in the sought after Frances Arbor community in Temple Terrace. This home sits on an oversized 1/3rd acre corner lot and features over 3,000 heated square feet with and features 5 generous sized bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a huge 2-story pool cage, an oversized 2 car side entry garage, a 2nd floor balcony, beautiful grand oak trees, and the owner has taken care of all the big ticket items…This First and foremost YOU WILL NOT HAVE AN ELECTRIC BILL HERE…imagine the savings!! the seller had a $65k top of the line Solar system with 45 solar panels and a 24kw battery backup, so you will NEVER LOSE POWER. There is also a BACKUP 14kw GENERATOR in case you have no power from loss of the sun that will rechargeable the batteries. Last year more power was sent to TECO than RECEIVED!! Additional items: 1.5-year-old roof with upgraded peel and stick underlayment, 2 new 21 seer 3 stage AC units, new saltwater pool chlorinator, new high efficiency water heater, new whole home water filtration system and water softener, new refrigerator, gas stove-top, dishwasher, wine cooler, and vent fan. All new flooring installed in the entire home except main living area, new comfort height toilets, newly added R48 insulation, new vinyl fence, all trees have been trimmed back, app controlled watering system, and there is so much more you are going to fall in love with. From the moment you walk through the front door, you will see how special this home is. When you enter the double front door into the home, you will notice the open floor plan and towering ceilings in the great room. There are a ton of windows throughout that keep this home light and bright. This home kitchen was renovated with custom made solid oak kitchen cabinets by master carpenters, granite counters and stainless appliances. A chef’s dream kitchen with plenty of room to cook, seating located at the island allows guests to participate while over-looking the lush back yard and pool/spa area. The living room and dining room have a wide-open floor plan great for entertaining! The upstairs master bath has an oversized walk-in shower with high quality tiles and a marble counter tops with double sinks. The first floor ensuite bedroom is perfect for guest privacy and extended family members. The second story offers 2 balconies that overlook the pool, perfect for morning coffee. Top of the line carpet in all of the bedrooms and strand woven bamboo/tile in the main living areas. All three and half bathrooms have been updated with granite counters and upgraded tiles. The garage also has an EV CHARGING RECEPTICLE. Where else can you find over a 1/3rd acre lot on tree lined streets, located in one of the best neighborhoods in charming, historic Temple Terrace. This home is a walk, bike or golf cart ride away from all local amenities, including numerous parks, schools, the Rec Center and Temple Terrace Country Club. The Temple Terrace Rec Center has activities for all ages; from multiples pools, indoor basketball and a gymnastics center to tennis, volleyball, exercise classes and kid’s sports leagues. Temple Terrace is a family-friendly haven and offers community festivals and parades throughout the year, it is also centrally located in Tampa; being just minutes from University of South Florida, Interstate 75, and a 20-minute commute to Downtown Tampa, 45 minutes to MacDill Air Force Base.
